<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>El Prode Mundialista</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f6f9fe;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --panel-soft: #f7fbff;
      --line: #d8e4f2;
      --line-strong: #c7d7ea;
      --text: #14314f;
      --muted: #6e829c;
      --accent: #2364ff;
      --accent-2: #4cb4ff;
      --accent-soft: #eaf2ff;
      --good: #13986d;
      --warn: #c57e00;
      --danger: #d94f63;
      --shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(20, 49, 79, 0.10);
      --radius: 24px;
      --radius-sm: 18px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(35,100,255,0.08), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(76,180,255,0.14), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fbfdff 0%, #eef5fc 100%);
    }

    body { padding: 0; }

    .shell {
      width: min(1280px, calc(100% - 24px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 18px 0 96px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero-card, .card {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 22px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      content: "⚽";
      position: absolute;
      right: 18px;
      top: 8px;
      font-size: 72px;
      opacity: 0.07;
      transform: rotate(-10deg);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px solid #d5e4ff;
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff, #f9fcff);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      min-width: 210px;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 74px;
      height: 74px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f5bff, #58beff);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(35,100,255,0.18);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .logo-mark svg {
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      display: block;
    }

    .logo-text-box {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .logo-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .logo-caption {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px);
      line-height: 1.02;
    }

    .subtitle {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 760px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .rules {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .rule-pill {
      background: var(--panel-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      min-height: 84px;
    }

    .rule-pill strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .rule-pill span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .auth-card {
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .auth-title, .section-title {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .auth-title h2, .section-title h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    input, select, button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    input[type="text"], input[type="number"], select {
      width: 100%;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      outline: none;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus {
      border-color: rgba(35,100,255,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(35,100,255,0.10);
    }

    button {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    }

    button:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    button:disabled { opacity: 0.58; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }

    .btn-primary {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(35,100,255,0.18);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--text);
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    }

    .btn-google {
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 52px;
      width: 100%;
      color: var(--text);
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    }

    .topbar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr auto auto;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      min-height: 52px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(20, 49, 79, 0.05);
    }

    .view-tabs {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .view-tab {
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 50px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .view-tab.active {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      border-color: transparent;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(35,100,255,0.15);
    }

    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .tab {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .tab.active {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      border-color: transparent;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(35,100,255,0.15);
    }

    .view-panel {
      display: none;
    }

    .view-panel.active {
      display: block;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .summary-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .summary-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fbff 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .summary-card .value {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 8px 0 4px;
    }

    .summary-card .label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .cards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .fixture-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .argentina-highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef7ff, #ffffff);
      border-color: #cfe3ff;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .fixture-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .match-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fbff 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .match-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .match-body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .team {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .team.right {
      justify-content: flex-end;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .flag {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      position: relative;
    }

    .flag-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .flag-fallback {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: none;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .mini-flag {
      width: 18px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      display: inline-grid;
      place-items: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
      position: relative;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .mini-flag img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .mini-flag .flag-fallback {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .inline-flag-pair {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .team-name {
      font-weight: 800;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .team-meta {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .score-box {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .score-box input {
      width: 68px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 6px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .score-sep {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .deadline-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .match-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .tag.good {
      color: #0c6e4d;
      border-color: #b6e6d0;
      background: #ebfaf3;
    }

    .tag.warn {
      color: #8f6205;
      border-color: #f0d39d;
      background: #fff6e4;
    }

    .tag.accent {
      color: var(--accent);
      border-color: #d4e4ff;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .tag.bad {
      color: #a53445;
      border-color: #f0c0c8;
      background: #fff1f3;
    }

    .notice {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff7df;
      border: 1px solid #efd18b;
      color: #8a6200;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .panel-note, .empty {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px dashed var(--line-strong);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .standings-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .standings-table th,
    .standings-table td {
      padding: 12px 10px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .standings-table th {
      color: #60748f;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: #f7fbff;
    }

    .standings-table tr.highlight {
      background: #eef5ff;
    }

    .fixture-mini, .fixture-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .fixture-mini:last-child,
    .fixture-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .fixture-day {
      padding: 14px 0 4px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .bracket-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .bracket-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      min-width: 1360px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .bracket-column {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .bracket-column:not(:last-child)::after {
      content: '→';
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      right: -12px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 900;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .bracket-round-title {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff, #f9fcff);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .bracket-round-title small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .bracket-match {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fbff 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(20,49,79,0.06);
    }

    .bracket-match.final {
      border-color: #d4e4ff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff, #ffffff);
    }

    .bracket-match-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .bracket-team {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .bracket-team:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .bracket-note {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .admin-box {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .result-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(35,100,255,0.16);
    }

    .mobile-nav {
      position: fixed;
      left: 12px;
      bottom: max(12px, env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
      transform: none;
      width: min(calc(100% - 24px), 420px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(199,215,234,0.95);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(20,49,79,0.16);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 8px;
      display: none;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      z-index: 20;
    }

    .mobile-nav button {
      min-height: 58px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      padding: 8px 4px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .mobile-nav button.active {
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border-color: #d7e5ff;
    }

    .hidden { display: none !important; }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero, .grid, .topbar, .cards-grid, .summary-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .view-tabs {
        display: none;
      }
      .mobile-nav {
        display: grid;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .shell {
        width: min(100% - 16px, 1280px);
        padding-top: 12px;
      }

      .hero-card, .card, .auth-card, .summary-card {
        padding: 16px;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }

      .rules { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .match-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .team.right { justify-content: flex-start; text-align: left; }
      .score-box { justify-content: space-between; }
      .score-box input { width: 100%; }
      .match-footer { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .match-footer button { width: 100%; }
      .standings-table th:nth-child(4),
      .standings-table td:nth-child(4),
      .standings-table th:nth-child(5),
      .standings-table td:nth-child(5) {
        display: none;
      }
      .logo-wrap { width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-app-compat.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-auth-compat.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.12.2/firebase-firestore-compat.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="hero-top">
          <div>
            <div class="brand-badge">🧉⚽ El Prode Mundialista</div>
            <h1>La quiniela mundialera de la familia.</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
              Una app familiar, argenta y fácil de usar desde el celu: entrás con Google, ves el resumen, seguís la tabla, apostás por fecha y revisás el fixture del Mundial 2026 con banderas reales.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="logo-wrap" aria-label="Logo de El Prode Mundialista">
            <div class="logo-mark">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="jpCup" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffffff" stop-opacity="0.96" />
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e8f3ff" stop-opacity="0.92" />
                  </linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" />
                <path d="M22 16h20v6c0 7-4.7 12.5-10 14.1-5.3-1.6-10-7.1-10-14.1z" fill="url(#jpCup)" />
                <path d="M18 18h4v5c0 3.8-2.7 7-6.4 7.7L14 31v-4.5c2.3-.4 4-2.2 4-4.5z" fill="url(#jpCup)" />
                <path d="M46 18h4v4.5c0 2.3 1.7 4.1 4 4.5V31l-1.6-.3C48.7 30 46 26.8 46 23z" fill="url(#jpCup)" />
                <rect x="29" y="36" width="6" height="8" rx="2" fill="url(#jpCup)" />
                <rect x="22" y="44" width="20" height="5" rx="2.5" fill="url(#jpCup)" />
                <path d="M24 24h6v4h-6zM34 24h6v4h-6z" fill="#1f5bff" opacity="0.65" />
                <path d="M27 19c2.2 1 4 2.8 5 5 1-2.2 2.8-4 5-5-2.2-1-4-2.8-5-5-1 2.2-2.8 4-5 5z" fill="#58beff" opacity="0.95" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-text-box">
              <div class="logo-title">El Prode Mundialista</div>
              <div class="logo-caption">Mundial 2026 · familia, puntos y gloria casera · edición jp_renegado</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rules">
          <div class="rule-pill">
            <strong>🎯 4 puntos por exacto</strong>
            <span>Si acertás el marcador completo del partido.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-pill">
            <strong>✅ 2 puntos por signo</strong>
            <span>Si acertás ganador o empate, aunque no lo claves exacto.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-pill">
            <strong>🏁 Jugar siempre suma</strong>
            <span>Si apostaste y no acertaste, sumás 1. Si no jugaste ese partido, sumás 0.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-card hero-card">
        <div class="auth-title">
          <h2>🔐 Acceso</h2>
          <span class="small">Google + Firebase</span>
        </div>

        <div id="setupNotice" class="notice hidden"></div>

        <div class="row">
          <button id="googleLoginBtn" class="btn-google">
            <span>🟢</span>
            <span>Entrar con Google</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div id="signedInBox" class="hidden">
          <div class="row">
            <div id="userAvatar" class="avatar">J</div>
            <div>
              <div id="authUserName" style="font-weight: 800;">Juan Pablo</div>
              <div id="authUserEmail" class="small">usuario@email.com</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="small">Tu pronóstico queda guardado por usuario y se comparte con toda la familia. Exacto = 4, signo = 2, fallo con apuesta = 1, sin jugar = 0.</div>
        </div>

        <div id="signedOutHint" class="small hidden">
          Entrá con Google para que cada familiar tenga su usuario y su tabla.
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <button id="logoutBtn" class="btn-secondary">Cerrar sesión</button>
        </div>

        <div class="small">
          Si todavía no pegaste tu configuración, la app entra en <strong>modo demo local</strong>. El login real y el backend se activan completando <code>FIREBASE_CONFIG</code> y habilitando Google en Firebase Authentication.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div id="appContent">
      <section class="topbar">
        <div class="pill"><span>🙋</span><strong id="currentUserLabel">Juan Pablo</strong></div>
        <div class="pill"><span>📅</span><span id="nextMatchLabel">Próximo partido</span></div>
        <div class="pill"><span>⭐</span><span id="userPointsLabel">0 pts</span></div>
        <button id="refreshBtn" class="btn-secondary">Actualizar</button>
      </section>

      <section class="view-tabs" id="viewTabs">
        <button class="view-tab active" data-view="resumen">🏠 Resumen</button>
        <button class="view-tab" data-view="apuestas">🎯 Apuestas</button>
        <button class="view-tab" data-view="clasificacion">🥇 Clasificación</button>
